### Daily/Weekly Bookkeeping Checklist
```markdown
# Bookkeeping Task Checklist

## Daily Tasks
- [ ] Check bank accounts for transactions
- [ ] Record incoming payments received
- [ ] Process and record invoices to pay
- [ ] Record credit card charges
- [ ] Respond to vendor/customer inquiries
- [ ] Back up accounting files

## Weekly Tasks

### Monday
- [ ] Download bank transactions
- [ ] Categorize and record transactions
- [ ] Review open AP invoices
- [ ] Schedule payment runs

### Tuesday
- [ ] Process payroll (if applicable)
- [ ] Record payroll journal entry
- [ ] Submit payroll tax deposits
- [ ] Update employee expense reports

### Wednesday
- [ ] Generate customer invoices
- [ ] Send AR statements (if applicable)
- [ ] Follow up on past due receivables
- [ ] Process credit memos/adjustments

### Thursday
- [ ] Review credit card statements
- [ ] Categorize credit card expenses
- [ ] Process expense reimbursements
- [ ] Update vendor files

### Friday
- [ ] AP payment run
- [ ] Record payments in system
- [ ] Weekly cash reconciliation
- [ ] Prepare weekly cash report
- [ ] File documents for the week

## Month-End Tasks

### First Week of Month
- [ ] Complete bank reconciliations
- [ ] Complete credit card reconciliations
- [ ] Process final invoices for prior month
- [ ] Cut off AP for prior month

### Reconciliations
- [ ] Operating bank account
- [ ] Payroll bank account
- [ ] Credit card accounts
- [ ] Petty cash (if applicable)

### Accruals and Adjustments
- [ ] Prepaid expense amortization
- [ ] Accrued expenses review
- [ ] Revenue recognition review
- [ ] Fixed asset additions/depreciation

### Reporting Preparation
- [ ] Trial balance review
- [ ] AR aging report
- [ ] AP aging report
- [ ] Supporting schedules
```

