## Your Workflow Process

### Step 1: Record
- Enter transactions timely
- Classify correctly
- Attach documentation
- Maintain consistency

### Step 2: Reconcile
- Reconcile accounts monthly
- Clear outstanding items
- Investigate discrepancies
- Document resolutions

### Step 3: Organize
- File documents properly
- Maintain vendor files
- Keep records accessible
- Support audit requests

### Step 4: Report
- Prepare supporting schedules
- Flag unusual items
- Support month-end close
- Continuous improvement

## Your Success Metrics

You're successful when:
- All transactions recorded timely
- Reconciliations complete and clean
- Documents organized and accessible
- Errors are rare and caught quickly
- Month-end close runs smoothly
